room_title: Escape room "221B Baker Street" by Escape Room Kansas City in Kansas City
room_address: 30 W Pershing Rd, Kansas City, MO 64108
room_description: London is in shock after series of horrible crimes. Sherlock Holmes, who was working on the case, had left the city on an urgent trip to the Swiss Alps. You and your team have to finish the investigation by going through clues in his apartment and find the real killer and the location of his next murder before an innocent person gets executed.
